Responsive Pricing Tables for WordPress</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2014/06/23/caspar-huebinger-wordpress-on-fait-speak-my-language-va-bene/\' title=\'\'>WordPress.tv: Caspar Hübinger: WordPress, On Fait Speak My Language, Va Bene?</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2014/06/23/forrer-sebel-oop-in-wordpress-themes/\' title=\'\'>WordPress.tv: Tom Forrer and Michael Sebel: OOP In WordPress Themes</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li class=\'dashboard-news-plugin\'><span>Plugin popular:</span> <a href=\'http://wordpress.org/plugins/better-wp-security/\' class=\'dashboard-news-plugin-link\'>iThemes Security (formerly Better WP Security)</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=better-wp-security&amp;_wpnonce=9631610e10&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'iThemes Security (formerly Better WP Security)\'>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>','no'),(1108,'_site_transient_timeout_poptags_40cd750bba9870f18aada2478b24840a','1403641086','yes'),(1109,'_site_transient_poptags_40cd750bba9870f18aada2478b24840a','a:40:{s:6:\"widget\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"widget\";s:4:\"slug\";s:6:\"widget\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"4463\";}s:4:\"post\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:4:\"Post\";s:4:\"slug\";s:4:\"post\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"2778\";}s:6:\"plugin\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:4:\"slug\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"2683\";}s:5:\"admin\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"admin\";s:4:\"slug\";s:5:\"admin\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"2196\";}s:5:\"posts\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"posts\";s:4:\"slug\";s:5:\"posts\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"2110\";}s:7:\"sidebar\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"sidebar\";s:4:\"slug\";s:7:\"sidebar\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"1756\";}s:6:\"google\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"google\";s:4:\"slug\";s:6:\"google\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"1553\";}s:7:\"twitter\";a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"twitter\";s:4:\"slug\";s:7:\"twitter\";s:5:\"count\";s:4:\"1513\";}